{"timestamp": "2026-06-24T15:34:18.031476", "direction": "JD_LLM_OUTPUT", "identifier": "single_jd", "data": "{\n  \"Job Title\": \"Omnichannel Expert\",\n  \"Customer Requisition ID\": \"\",\n  \"Diversity\": \"\",\n  \"Designation\": \"\",\n  \"Primary Skills\": [\n    \"Omnichannel Expert\",\n    \"Retail Domain Omni Channel Experience\",\n    \"Ability to drive the vision of Omnichannel for different types of retailers\",\n    \"Ability to create and deliver the seamless holistic experience\",\n    \"Ability to integrate applications for true omni-channel experiences\",\n    \"Ability to envision Agile omni channel strategy and development methodology\",\n    \"Identify benefits omnichannel marketing can offer to online brands\"\n  ],\n  \"Secondary Skills\": [\n    \"Ability to deliver bespoke consulting services for all categories of retail\",\n    \"Ability to keep pace with the changing trends in industry\",\n    \"Ability to deliver distinguished Omnichannel experiences to end customers\",\n    \"Thought leadership\",\n    \"Customer value delivery\",\n    \"Leadership level\",\n    \"Innovative solution\"\n  ],\n  \"Salary\": {\n    \"currency\": \"\",\n    \"range\": \"\",\n    \"unit\": \"\",\n    \"frequency\": \"\"\n  },\n  \"Job Type\": \"full time\",\n  \"Job Closure Date\": \"\",\n  \"Job Status\": \"\",\n  \"Position Type\": \"New role\",\n  \"Expected Revenue\": \"\",\n  \"Currency Option\": \"\",\n  \"Number of open positions\": \"1\",\n  \"Experience\": \"15+\",\n  \"Job Mode\": \"On Site\",\n  \"Industry\": \"Retail\",\n  \"Location\": \"Kolkata\",\n  \"Address\": \"\",\n  \"Zip Code\": \"\",\n  \"Qualification\": \"Bachelor's Degree\",\n  \"Job Description\": \"The Omnichannel Expert will be responsible for driving the vision of Omnichannel for various retailers across different channels, including physical stores, digital platforms, and marketplaces. This role involves delivering bespoke consulting services for diverse retail categories such as food, pharmacy, fashion, DIY, and general merchandise. The expert will focus on creating and delivering seamless, holistic customer experiences accessible at their fingertips. This includes integrating applications to achieve true omni-channel capabilities and envisioning Agile omni-channel strategies and development methodologies. The role also involves identifying the benefits of omnichannel marketing for online brands and suggesting strategies to convert customer journeys into sales. The ideal candidate will stay abreast of industry trends, anticipate market demands, and develop proactive strategies for omnichannel journeys. A key aspect of the role is delivering distinguished omnichannel experiences by deeply understanding customer behaviors and demographic diversity for different retailers. The position offers an opportunity to be part of a team that makes a significant impact at a leadership level within customer organizations, contributing to the creation and operationalization of strategies that deliver value. The role also involves conceiving, developing, and delivering innovative solutions, potentially leveraging TCS IP, TCS COIN partners, and strategic alliances, aiming to be a pioneer in industry communities for thought leadership and customer value delivery.\",\n  \"Roles and Responsibilities\": \"Drive the vision of Omnichannel for different types of retailers across channels - physical, digital, marketplaces etc. Deliver bespoke consulting services for all categories of retail - Food, Pharmacy, Fashion, DIY, Specialty and General Merchandise. Create and deliver the seamless holistic experience that connected customers want at their fingertips. Integrate applications for true omni-channel experiences. Envision Agile omni channel strategy and development methodology. Identify benefits omnichannel marketing can offer to online brands and suggest ways to deliver omnichannel journeys that convert into sales. Keep pace with the changing trends in industry and foresee the market demands and strategies for Omnichannel journeys much earlier than the competitors. Deliver distinguished Omnichannel experiences to end customers of retailers by deep learning of customer experiences and diversity of demography for different retailers. Be part of the team who will try to create an impact in customer landscape at a leadership level. Conceive, develop and deliver innovative solution with opportunity to bring TCS IP, TCS COIN partners and strategic partners. Be a pioneer in the industry communities for both thought leadership and customer value delivery.\",\n  \"Bucket\": \"Strategy & Consulting\"\n}"}
