{"timestamp": "2026-06-24T15:45:28.517838", "direction": "JD_LLM_OUTPUT", "identifier": "single_jd", "data": "{\n  \"Job Title\": \"Omnichannel Expert\",\n  \"Customer Requisition ID\": \"\",\n  \"Diversity\": \"\",\n  \"Designation\": \"\",\n  \"Primary Skills\": [\n    \"Retail Domain Omni Channel Experience\",\n    \"Omnichannel strategy\",\n    \"Omnichannel journeys\",\n    \"customer experiences\",\n    \"retailers\",\n    \"physical channels\",\n    \"digital channels\"\n  ],\n  \"Secondary Skills\": [\n    \"Ability to drive the vision of Omnichannel for different types of retailers across channels - physical, digital, marketplaces etc.\",\n    \"Ability to deliver bespoke consulting services for all categories of retail - Food, Pharmacy, Fashion, DIY, Specialty and General Merchandise\",\n    \"Ability to create and deliver the seamless holistic experience that connected customers want at their fingertips.\",\n    \"Ability to integrate applications for true omni-channel experiences\",\n    \"Ability to envision Agile omni channel strategy and development methodology\",\n    \"Identify benefits omnichannel marketing can offer to online brands and suggest ways to deliver omnichannel journeys that convert into sales\",\n    \"Ability to keep pace with the changing trends in industry and foresee the market demands and strategies for Omnichannel journeys much early than the competitors\",\n    \"Ability to deliver distinguished Omnichannel experiences to end customers of retailers by deep learning of customer experiences and diversity of demography for different retailers\"\n  ],\n  \"Salary\": {\n    \"currency\": \"\",\n    \"range\": \"\",\n    \"unit\": \"\",\n    \"frequency\": \"\"\n  },\n  \"Job Type\": \"full time\",\n  \"Job Closure Date\": \"\",\n  \"Job Status\": \"\",\n  \"Position Type\": \"New role\",\n  \"Expected Revenue\": \"\",\n  \"Currency Option\": \"\",\n  \"Number of open positions\": \"1\",\n  \"Experience\": \"15+\",\n  \"Job Mode\": \"On Site\",\n  \"Industry\": \"Retail\",\n  \"Location\": \"Kolkata\",\n  \"Address\": \"\",\n  \"Zip Code\": \"\",\n  \"Qualification\": \"Bachelor of Business Administration\",\n  \"Job Description\": \"The Omnichannel Expert will be responsible for driving the vision of Omnichannel for different types of retailers across channels, including physical, digital, and marketplaces. This role involves delivering bespoke consulting services for various retail categories and creating seamless, holistic customer experiences. The expert will also be responsible for integrating applications for true omni-channel experiences and envisioning Agile omni-channel strategy and development methodology. Identifying the benefits of omnichannel marketing and suggesting ways to convert journeys into sales is crucial. The role requires staying updated with industry trends, foreseeing market demands, and delivering distinguished omnichannel experiences by understanding customer experiences and demographic diversity.\",\n  \"Roles and Responsibilities\": \"Drive the vision of Omnichannel for different types of retailers across channels - physical, digital, marketplaces etc. Deliver bespoke consulting services for all categories of retail - Food, Pharmacy, Fashion, DIY, Specialty and General Merchandise. Create and deliver the seamless holistic experience that connected customers want at their fingertips. Integrate applications for true omni-channel experiences. Envision Agile omni channel strategy and development methodology. Identify benefits omnichannel marketing can offer to online brands and suggest ways to deliver omnichannel journeys that convert into sales. Keep pace with the changing trends in industry and foresee the market demands and strategies for Omnichannel journeys much early than the competitors. Deliver distinguished Omnichannel experiences to end customers of retailers by deep learning of customer experiences and diversity of demography for different retailers.\",\n  \"Bucket\": \"Strategy & Consulting\"\n}"}
