{"timestamp": "2026-06-25T16:17:54.362639", "direction": "JD_BUILDER_INPUT", "identifier": "raw_text_received", "data": "Job Description \u2013 Senior React \nDeveloper\nLocation: On-site\nDepartment: Technology / Frontend Engineering\nExperience Required: 5\u20137 years in Frontend Development (with at least 4 years in \nReact.js)\nAbout the Role\nWe are looking for a highly skilled Senior React Developer to join our growing technology \nteam. The ideal candidate should have extensive experience building scalable, high-\nperformance web applications using React.js and related technologies. Experience in \nintegrating AI-powered features and working with AI-driven APIs will be a strong plus. This \nrole will involve working closely with designers, backend engineers, and product managers \nto deliver seamless, intelligent user experiences.\nKey Responsibilities\n\u25cf\nDesign, develop, and maintain modern web applications using React.js, Next.js (if \napplicable), and supporting libraries.\n\u25cf\nWrite clean, reusable, and efficient code following best practices.\n\u25cf\nCollaborate with UX/UI designers to translate designs and wireframes into \nresponsive, high-quality code.\n\u25cf\nOptimize applications for maximum performance and scalability.\n\u25cf\nMentor and guide junior developers, conduct code reviews, and ensure coding \nstandards.\n\u25cf\nWork closely with backend teams to integrate RESTful APIs, GraphQL, and AI/ML \nAPIs (OpenAI.).\n\u25cf\nImplement AI-driven UI features (e.g., chatbots, auto-suggestions, personalization, \nanalytics dashboards).\n\u25cf\nDebug, troubleshoot, and improve existing applications.\n\u25cf\nStay up to date with the latest trends in frontend technologies and AI-enhanced \nfrontend development.\nRequired Skills & Qualifications\n\u25cf\nStrong proficiency in JavaScript (ES6+), React.js, and Redux/Context API.\n\u25cf\nHands-on experience with React Hooks, Next.js, or other modern frameworks.\n\u25cf\nStrong understanding of HTML5, CSS3, and responsive design.\n\u25cf\nFamiliarity with TypeScript is highly desirable.\n\u25cf\nExperience integrating with REST APIs and/or GraphQL.\n\u25cf\nSolid understanding of frontend build tools (Webpack, Babel, Vite, etc.).\n\u25cf\nExperience with unit testing frameworks (Jest, React Testing Library).\n\u25cf\nFamiliarity with CI/CD pipelines and Git-based workflows.\n\u25cf\nStrong problem-solving and debugging skills.\nNice-to-Have Skills\n\u25cf\nExperience with React Native or mobile-first development.\n\u25cf\nKnowledge of micro-frontends architecture.\n\u25cf\nFamiliarity with cloud platforms (AWS/GCP/Azure), especially AI/ML services like \nAWS Sagemaker, GCP Vertex AI, or Azure OpenAI.\n\u25cf\nExposure to Agile/Scrum methodologies."}
